usage.body:
We use the data you share with us solely to:

· respond to enquiries submitted through the contact form;
· maintain the security and stability of the site;
· anonymously analyse usage patterns to improve content and the user experience (only with your consent).

rights.body:
Under GDPR you have the right to:

· access the personal data we hold about you;
· rectify inaccurate data;
· erase your data (right to be forgotten);
· restrict processing;
· data portability;
· object to processing;
· withdraw consent at any time.

To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the email below. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Bulgarian Commission for Personal Data Protection (CPDP).
